{
  "stem": "9102.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they must have taken care of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But that's beside the point.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then gradually, I could-- you know, my family became smaller and smaller.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandparents from my father's side were picked up, put up there, downtown, and then put into transportation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father found out, and he went down to the, uh, building where they are all housed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was trying to get them out, to buy them out one way or another.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was picked up and put on transport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he escaped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came home one night, all damaged and band-- wounded because he had jumped out of the train going down to, I guess, Westerbork or whatever concentration camp there was in Holland.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they went from there to Czechoslovakia, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The idea was, what I was told that-- no, not often, but-- they wanted to exchange the Jewish people from Poland with the ones in Holland.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what-- why they put those, picked up the people, just to bring them-- that's what we were told by the Germans and by the news media there in Holland.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They just wanted to exchange them, bring the Polish Jewish over to Holland, and we had to go to Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, maybe in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because at that time they asked for volunteers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know none of my family ever-- you know, relatives, went as volunteers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not till they were picked up later on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, for my mo-- uh, my mother's side it was Jonas and Betty, Betje.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father's side was Leopold, what I am called after, and my grandmother was Judy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My parent's grandp-- uh, my father's grandp-- my father's parents were picked up, you know, relatively early in the season.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
